Notes: UWSP is ranked 4th and UWEC is ranked 22nd in latest D3 hoops.com poll. With
UWSP leading 40-35 with 13:06 left in 2nd half, EC went on a 10-2 run to take
a 45-42 lead with 09:35. Leafblad lead the way during the run with 2 3's. UWSP
took a 56-55 lead with 2:30 left but EC hit 5-8 FT in final 20 seconds.
